connect20/aftership.name: connect20/aftership

suggest.magento-hackathon/magento-composer-insta: Allows to manage this package as a dependency

connect20/aftership.description:
AfterShip magento extension interface. Tracking number will be added to the aftership.com http://aftership.com/
 account at the same time when input in magento shipment. Please go to aftership.com http://aftership.com/
  to change the notification setting and value.
